Laika Installation
==================

First Install LIBFTDI:

apt-get update

apt-get upgrade

apt-get install libftdi-dev

Install Laika by typing:
=======================

cd~

wget --no-check-certificate https://github.com/eightdog/laika/archive/1.0.0-beta.tar.gz

tar -xzf laika-1.0.0-beta.tar.gz

cd laika-1.0.0/build

chmod a+x build.sh 

./build.sh


Then test by browsing to laika-1.0.0/source/examples/py_test

and type:

python example_1.py

This should run the LED's and verify a connection.
